      "body": "Hi Alex,\n\nI hope this email finds you well. I'm forwarding this email regarding the collaboration between Marketing and IT that we've been discussing. It’s crucial to align our teams to streamline processes and enhance communication, especially as we move forward with the Q1 initiatives.\n\nAs you know, the primary focus for the next quarter is improving the customer acquisition strategy by integrating advanced analytics tools with our marketing campaigns. IT's expertise will be invaluable in ensuring smooth deployment and operation of these tools.\n\nPlease let me know your availability next week to discuss this further, and I’ll coordinate with the IT team to set up a joint meeting. In the meantime, if you have any immediate thoughts or concerns, feel free to share them with me.\n\nLooking forward to collaborating on this.\n\nBest regards,  \nJane\n"
    }
